"The virus 'W32.Nimda.A@mm' is present on the remote host\n",
"Solution : http://www.symantec.com/avcenter/venc/data/w32.nimda.a@mm.html\n",
"Risk factor : High");
 
  security_hole(port:port, data:report);
 }
}
 
